VAC-47413HSSE Manager - Operator - UAE / Yemen - Expatriate Opportunity
A leading international oil company seek a HSSE Manager to be based in the UAE , with business travel to Yemen.The ideal candidate will:" Be Degree Qualified " Have 15 - 20 years Oil & Gas experience (minimum 10 years in HSSE)" Experience of managing Security measures in hostile locations " Have practical knowledge of Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR) matters" International work experience within Exploration & Production operationsThis is an exciting opportunity to join a market leader at a key stage of growth, a highly competitive expatriate package is available on single or family status.
